media.headline: Stroman's first strikeout of '17

media.headline: Stroman fans the side in the 1st

media.bigblurb: Marcus Stroman fans Evan Longoria to strike out the side in order and end the 1st inning

media.headline: Kid showcases impressive skills

media.headline: Souza Jr. injured at home

media.bigblurb: Steven Souza Jr. is shaken up after a collision with the catcher at home plate while trying to score in the bottom of the 5th

media.headline: Martin scores on squeeze play

media.headline: Miller scores on wild pitch

media.bigblurb: Brad Miller crosses the plate on a wild pitch in the 9th inning, cutting the Rays' deficit to 5-2

media.headline: Snell's first strikeout of 2017

media.bigblurb: Blue Jays manager John Gibbons discusses Marcus Stroman and Joe Biagini's performances and Kendrys Morales' hitting in the team's 5-2 win
